Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Formatter
    The Formatter class is used to "standardize" the format of the tokens that are the result of the wordBreak method of the WordSegmentation class.
    Node
    The Node object is the basic component of the Trie data structure.
    SMSQuery
    The SMSQuery class is responsible for the database access.
    StatChecker
    The StatChecker class is another one of the debugging tools developed for the system.
    Tester
    The Tester class is a debugging class made to check the intermediate steps during the wordBreak method.
    Trie
    The Trie class is the underlying data structure for the dictionary of the system.
    TrieBuilder
    The TrieBuilder class allows the system to preprocess the dictionary into a Trie data structure.
    TrieReader
    The TrieReader's readTrie method is called upon initializing the system.
    Version
    The Version class is used for debugging purposes only and is not really part of the system.
    WordSegmentation
    The WordSegmentation class is responsible for the parsing and correcting of the SMS messages given a Trie object.
